name: flake8-builtins
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "flake8-builtins" %}
{% set version = "1.5.3" %}
{% set sha256 = "09998853b2405e98e61d2ff3027c47033adbdc17f9fe44ca58443d876eb00f3b" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - flake8

test:
  commands:
    - 'flake8 --version | grep flake8_builtins:'

about:
  home: https://github.com/gforcada/flake8-builtins
  license: GPL-2.0
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Check for python builtins being used as variables or parameters.
  dev_url: https://github.com/gforcada/flake8-builtins

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dopplershift
smithy_version:
